  "prompt": "Who provides the best Digital Marketing Classes in Pune?",
  "response": "As of my last update, Pune is home to several reputable institutions and training centers that offer digital marketing courses. Some of the well-regarded options include:\n\n1. **Digital Vidya**: Known for its comprehensive curriculum and experienced trainers, Digital Vidya offers various courses, workshops, and certifications in digital marketing.\n\n2. **SEED Infotech**: This institute offers a range of professional courses, including a well-structured digital marketing program that covers SEO, SEM, social media, and more.\n\n3. **LIPS India (Lavenir Institute of Professional Studies)**: LIPS India is known for its practical approach to digital marketing education, focusing on real-world applications.\n\n4. **PIIDM (Pune Institute of Internet & Digital Marketing)**: PIIDM offers an extensive digital marketing course that covers all major aspects of the field, with an emphasis on practical training.\n\n5. **Digital Trainee**: Offering hands-on training and real-time project work, Digital Trainee is a popular choice for beginners looking to break into the digital marketing industry.\n\n6. **Academy of Digital Marketing**: This academy provides curated courses designed to meet industry requirements and prepare students for careers in digital marketing.\n\n7. **NSDM India (National School of Internet Marketing)**: Known for their live projects and internship opportunities, NSDM India provides in-depth digital marketing courses.\n\nAttending a demo class, exploring course content, and checking reviews can help you decide which course best suits your needs.",
